00:19:45.322 --> 00:19:46.615
Hai!

00:19:47.419 --> 00:19:48.554
Di mana?

00:19:49.036 --> 00:19:50.249
Semuanya baik-baik saja?

00:19:51.009 --> 00:19:53.265
