00:19:54.879 --> 00:19:56.234
Dimana Mega?

00:19:56.953 --> 00:19:58.364
Oke.

00:19:58.774 --> 00:20:00.430
Kamu berhati-hati, oke?

00:20:01.320 --> 00:20:02.481
